               stealing, on the <rs id="t18261026-179-cd998" type="crimeDate">12th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261026-179-off997 t18261026-179-cd998"></join>, 2 live pigs, price 3l.
            </rs>, the property of 
               <persName id="t18261026-179-victim1082" type="victimName">
                  William Henry 
                  Bain
               <interp inst="t18261026-179-victim1082" type="surname" value="Bain"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18261026-179-victim1082" type="given" value="William Henry"></interp>
